169
00:13:17,776 --> 00:13:20,377
Um, Premier Ryzhkov
has determined that...

170
00:13:20,379 --> 00:13:22,749
<i>If he determined, then he determined.</i>

171
00:13:22,752 --> 00:13:24,280
<i>Look, Professor Legasov,</i>

172
00:13:24,282 --> 00:13:26,383
<i>you are there for one reason only.</i>

173
00:13:26,385 --> 00:13:28,519
<i>Do you understand? To make this stop.</i>

174
00:13:28,521 --> 00:13:29,920
