242
00:18:29,880 --> 00:18:31,547
Not on paper.

243
00:18:33,017 --> 00:18:34,950
Everyone who was in the control room,

244
00:18:34,952 --> 00:18:37,353
Dyatlov, Akimov, Toptunov,

245
